concept_datatype.name: Coded
concept_datatype.description: Value determined by term dictionary lookup (i.e., term identifier)

concept_datatype.description: Pointer to a binary or text-based document (e.g., clinical document, RTF, XML, EKG, image, etc.) stored in complex_obs table

concept_description.description: Describes a cause of death for a patient. Coded answer.

A treatment status, indicating that the patient is being followed, but is not yet on treatment
Indicates that the patient has been cured of the relevant disease
Used by athletes after sporting events
